snippet.title: WaveTiles Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Add WaveTiles to your wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1576540

Also, make sure to get notified for the upcoming Kickstarter campaign launch!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/whocaresgames/wavetiles

WaveTiles is a two-player co-op puzzle platformer and will be WhoCares Games' debut title when it launches on Steam later this year!

Follow us on social media to stay updated!
https://www.facebook.com/WhoCaresGames
http://instagram.com/WhoCaresGames
